{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/Header_Gif_Steam.gif?t=1737835955\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Angels &amp; Demons is a multi-genre mash-up!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The barrier separating The Living Realm from The Spiritual Realm has been broken!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's up to you, your guardian angel Yui, and some of your friends to fix it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/BarrierSteam.png?t=1737835955\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/GameplayHeader_Steam.png?t=1737835955\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the overworld, you can make use of all kinds of different abilities. Some shared, and some unique to specific characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel the world on your quest to save the world from demons of The Seven Deadly Sins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/Platformer_GifSteam.gif?t=1737835955\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight off enemies in turn-based battles! Each character has their own unique set of strengths, weaknesses, and special attacks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/RPG_Gif_Steam.gif?t=1737835955\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But when the enemy has a chance to attack, you'll have to dodge using one of multiple different &quot;Attack Styles!&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With 14 different attack styles, there's TONS of variety in enemy attacks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/AttackStylesSteam.gif?t=1737835955\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Oh yeah, this is a rhythm game too!</h2></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tons of overworld elements sync to the music, certain attacks are music synced too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There's also a full-on mania-style rhythm game featuring 20 different tracks, each with four different difficulties!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Difficulties friendly to beginners and experts alike!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/Rhythm_Gif_Steam.gif?t=1737835955\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/MultiplayerSteam.png?t=1737835955\" />Play with your friends! 5 player local co-op! 5 player online versus!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(and 4 player offline versus, because the screen would be too cramped otherwise!) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/extras/MultiplayerGifSteam.gif?t=1737835955\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737835955","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/page.bg.jpg?t=1737835955","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737835955","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198290/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737835955","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared